<br>
And remember, if you are in a LDoN with a group who has two (2) melee members who can't hold aggro or regain it after they need a complete heal to save their worthless butts and then blame the cleric for messing up the fight by healing and getting aggro then there is no buff that you can use that will make them any less pitiful than they are and will continue to be, and yes, this is a runon sentence, and yes, it is a sneaky way to slide a small rant into an unrelated thread.<br>
