<br>
I would just be honest with them at the buffing stage before you head in.  Some people don't realize, some need reminding... but if you just nicely say &quot;Hey all... I can cast Temperance, but I don't want to cast on folks who don't need it because it costs me about 11pp per cast.  Do you want me to do everyone, and maybe get some dot money at the end before the split?  Or should I just temp the tank? *smile*&quot;<br>
