Just be warned, some people might not understand how expensive it can be, or they might add other expenses onto it (e.g. &quot;Hey, you know, I spent 35pp worth of arrows!&quot; ) .. if it gets down to it, an easier thing might be to spend a few moments at the end of the adventure and ask &quot;Who needs reimbursements for reagents?&quot; .. At least that way everyone is covered.<br>
<br>
You should find it easier to stay ahead of the cost when you hit 49th level and get your 90 per cent resurrection. I usually don't ask for a cut of the dungeon revenue because if I spend a half hour in the Plane of Knowledge I can usually get at least one or two resurrection requests and they might pay anywhere from 50pp to 100pp.<br>
<br>
